{"tid":1562210,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無視中美貿戰　京東預約 iPhone 11 Pro 數量超 iPhone 11","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:32.000Z","uid":1121,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5443ef64ff4763a6cc2ccaceb4bbb57916561a0","tid":1562210,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"中美貿戰會影響 iPhone 銷量嗎？也許從京東昨天預約搶購 iPhone 的數字，令 Apple 感到安心。昨天京東開始接預約 iPhone 11 系列手機，只是一天裡便有近 100 萬部手機被預約。<br />\n<br />\n人們認為售價最相宜的 iPhone 11 銷情會是最好，但從預約的初部數字所見，iPhone 11 Pro 已達 49 萬台，隨後的 iPhone 11 為 30 萬台，至於 iPhone Pro Max 則為 11 萬台。顯示，在中國首輪 iPhone 開售以 iPhone 11 Pro 的購買意欲最強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ScreenShot190526013126-321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FScreenShot190526013126-321.jpg&h=a69485c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ScreenShot190526013126-320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FScreenShot190526013126-320.jpg&h=6a3e855a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ScreenShot190526013126-319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FScreenShot190526013126-319.jpg&h=4cfca2b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b59e20008769ffa17236e081e5cfe4cc9a11416a","tid":1562210,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong>